Based on this, the Cougar Dating App will provide opportunities for both groups of people to match, hook up and chat.

Someone can quickly expand their quality social network and meet like- minded elite & high value people. More importantly, you are both lovers of mature dating, and you will have a lot of common topics about your cougar life to share.

Our concept is "Brave to love, Don't Be Afraid of the Age Gap." Base on this concept, we develop a targeted algorithm system for the characteristics of age gap dating & mature dating. Its hookup and match features are more suitable for mature women and cougars.

The Cougar Dating - Mature Women App requires you to be at least 18 years old to use. Users must follow the rules of not sending offensive messages, hate speech, or uploading explicit content to our platform.
